{
  "texts": [
    "Haardt et al. 1994; Di Matteo 1998; Merloni and Fabian 2001).",
    "For decades, the geometry and extent of the corona was largely unknown, with arguments that it may be patchy, extend over parts of the inner disc, and vary with time (e.g.",
    "Gallo et al. 2015; Wilkins and Gallo 2015).",
    "However, spectral and timing studies suggest a compact, centrally located corona (e.g.",
    "Brenneman and Reynolds 2006; Fabian et al. 2009 Fabian et al., 2013;; Parker et al. 2015)."
  ]
}